{"serial": "26008", "department_serial": 25, "code": "OS2013", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Fundamentals of Electronics I", "ch": "基礎電學I"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Yang, Tsung-Hsun"], "ch": ["楊宗勳"]}, "credits": 4, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["5", "6"]}, "loc": {"building": "IL", "room": "203"}}, {"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "IL", "room": "203"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "光電科學與工程學系", "en": "Department of Optics and Photonics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "部分英語", "en": "Partially English"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 55, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程教導基本電路學及電子學理論，其中包括各種基本電子元件與電子電路分析之方法，是光電、電子及電機工程之重要基礎課程之一，同時為進階積體電路設計之先修課程。培養學生利用簡化等效模型等分析工具，瞭解熟悉各種基本電子元件的工作模式(包含二極體、電晶體、場效電晶體等)，以及相關的基礎應用 。", "en": "This course provides an introduction to the basic devices and circuits in modern electronics. Students will first learn basic electric circuits, semiconductor devices and circuits composing of diodes, BJTs and MOSFETs.  This is one of the fundamental and pre-requested courses in photonics, electronics and electrical engineering.Students will learn how to analyze the electronic circuits with equivalent models.  Some fundamental applications of the components will also be covered."}, "outline": {"ch": "1. 基本電路元件簡介\n- 電阻，電容，電感\n- 電路簡介\n2. 基本電路模型\n- 穩態/暫態電路分析\n- Laplace轉換及電路分析\n3. 基本放大器模型\n- 運算放大器基本應用\n- 頻率響應概念\n4. 二極體\n- 二極體電路分析\n- 二極體操作特性\n5. 雙極性接面電晶體\n- 接面電晶體特性\n- 接面電晶體放大器及邏輯電路應用\n- 接面電晶體小訊號模型分析 (放大器及頻率響應)\n6. 場效電晶體\n- 場效電晶體特性\n- 場效電晶體放大器及邏輯電路應用\n- 場效電晶體小訊號模型分析 (放大器及頻率響應)", "en": "1. IntroductionElectric Components:\n- Resistor, capacitance, and inductance\n- Circuit analysis\n2. Simple Circuit Model\n- Steady state / transient analysis\n- Laplace transformation\n3. Simple Amplifier Model\n- OP Amplifiers and circuit model\n- Single-time-constant (STC) frequency response\n4. Diodes\n- Junction diodes characteristics and rectifier circuit\n- Physical operation of pn junction\n5. Bipolar Junction Transistors (BJTs)\n- Device structure and physical operation\n- BJT amplifier small-signal operation\n6. MOS Field-Effect Transistors (MOSFETs)\n- Device structure and physical operation\n- BJT amplifier small-signal operation"}, "textbook": {"ch": "1. Microelectronic Circuits  8th edition, Sedra / Smith\n2. Fundamentals of Electric Circuits 5th edition, Charles Alexander, Matthew Sadiku \n3. Microelectronics  2nd edition, Behzad Razavi\n4. Electric Circuits  10th edition, James W. Nilsson, Susan Riedel", "en": "1. Microelectronic Circuits  8th edition, Sedra / Smith\n2. Fundamentals of Electric Circuits 5th edition, Charles Alexander, Matthew Sadiku \n3. Microelectronics  2nd edition, Behzad Razavi\n4. Electric Circuits  10th edition, James W. Nilsson, Susan Riedel"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "30", "en": "30"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n實習/實驗", "en": ["Lecture", "", "Practical Training Lab"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "1. Homework   –  25％\n2  期中考 × 2   –  25％ × 2\n3. 期末考　　  –  25％\n4. 缺席一次扣 10％", "en": "1. Homework           –  25％\n2  Mid-tem Exam.    –  25％ × 2\n3. Term Exam.　　  –  25％\n** Each absence will reduce the final grade by 10％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期二 3:00pm-4:00pm", "en": "Tuesday 3:00pm-4:00pm"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "模擬軟體自主學習", "en": "Self-directed learning with simulation software"}, "domain": {"ch": "基礎學科", "en": "基礎學科"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "專業知識", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "科學思辯", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "實驗能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "團隊合作", "rating": "(2)低", "assesments": ["作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"compe